308
00:20:50,249 --> 00:20:52,459
Mary Brunner, 26 anos.

309
00:20:53,335 --> 00:20:54,169
Bibliotecária.

310
00:20:55,045 --> 00:20:57,506
E Tex Watson, 24 anos.

311
00:20:58,423 --> 00:21:01,426
Aluno exemplar, editor 
