324
00:21:42,718 --> 00:21:44,344
Esta é a cena dos LaBianca.

325
00:21:45,137 --> 00:21:46,263
"Morte aos porcos."

326
00:21:47,806 --> 00:21:49,891
E na cena em Cielo Drive,

327
00:21:50,517 --> 00:21:52,894
"porco" com o sangue de Sharon Tate.

328
00:21:53,729 --> 00:21:54,938
Helter Skelter.

329
00:21:55,022 --> 00:21:56,565
Era o tema de Manson.

330
00:21:57,107 --> 00:21:58,317
A acusação

331
